OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778105470
OL,3,CThree people evacuated from hantavirus
OL,4,Cship amid Canary Islands row
OL,6,FThree suspected hantavirus patients
OL,7,Fhave been evacuated from an infected
OL,8,Fcruise ship off the coast of West
OL,9,FAfrica, the World Health Organisation
OL,10,F(WHO) has said.
OL,12,FThe British crew member, along with a
OL,13,FDutch colleague and another passenger,
OL,14,Fwere on their way to receive medical
OL,15,Fcare in the Netherlands, WHO director
OL,16,Fgeneral Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus
OL,17,Fsaid on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778105470
OL,3,CThree people evacuated from hantavirus
OL,4,Cship amid Canary Islands row
OL,6,F"WHO continues to work with the ship's
OL,7,Foperators to closely monitor the
OL,8,Fhealth of passengers and crew, working
OL,9,Fwith countries to support appropriate
OL,10,Fmedical follow-up and evacuation where
OL,11,Fneeded," he said.
OL,13,F"Monitoring and follow-up for
OL,14,Fpassengers on board and for those who
OL,15,Fhave already disembarked has been
OL,16,Finitiated in collaboration with the
OL,17,Fship's operators and national health
OL,18,Fauthorities."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778105470
OL,3,CThree people evacuated from hantavirus
OL,4,Cship amid Canary Islands row
OL,6,FThe latest update also follows a
OL,7,Fconfirmation of a fresh case of
OL,8,Fhantavirus among a former passenger
OL,9,Fwho had returned to Switzerland.
OL,11,FIt also comes amid a political row
OL,12,Fover whether the MV Hondius, which is
OL,13,Fcurrently docked off Cape Verde,
OL,14,Fshould be sent to the Canary Islands
OL,15,Ffollowing evacuations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778105470
OL,3,CThree people evacuated from hantavirus
OL,4,Cship amid Canary Islands row
OL,6,FFernando Clavijo, the leader of the
OL,7,FCanary Islands, an autonomous Spanish
OL,8,Fterritory, said he is opposed to the
OL,9,Fship docking there and has requested
OL,10,Fan urgent meeting with Spain's Prime
OL,11,FMinister Pedro Sanchez.
OL,13,FHis insistence on not accepting the
OL,14,Fvessel contradicts the Madrid
OL,15,Fgovernment, which said it would allow
OL,16,Fthe ship to dock in Tenerife, one of
OL,17,Fthe Canary Islands, in about three
OL,18,Fdays.
OL,26,@sD@Qrp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778105470
OL,3,CThree people evacuated from hantavirus
OL,4,Cship amid Canary Islands row
OL,6,F"We have no information whatsoever nor
OL,7,Fany official document from the
OL,8,Fgovernment," Clavijo told Spanish
OL,9,Fradio station Onda Cero.
OL,11,F"Without having information, I cannot
OL,12,Fallow them to enter the Canary
OL,13,FIslands, because we don't know what we
OL,14,Fare dealing with," added the
OL,15,Fterritory's president.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@LO]sD@AOUvD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
