CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778105470
OL,3,CThree people evacuated from hantavirus
OL,4,Cship amid Canary Islands row
OL,6,FIn a post on X, Clavijo wrote:
OL,7,F"Canarias always acts with
OL,8,Fresponsibility, but it cannot accept
OL,9,Fdecisions taken behind the backs of
OL,10,Fthe Canary Islands institutions and
OL,11,Fwithout sufficient information to the
OL,12,Fpopulation."
OL,14,FClavijo's comments same shortly before
OL,15,Fa fresh case of hantavirus was
OL,16,Fconfirmed in a former passenger who
OL,17,Fhad since returned to Switzerland.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
