OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778105470
OL,3,CThree people evacuated from hantavirus
OL,4,Cship amid Canary Islands row
OL,6,FIt brings the total number of cases to
OL,7,Feight, including three lab-confirmed
OL,8,Fcases and five suspected, including
OL,9,Fthree passengers who have died.
OL,11,FAuthorities in Switzerland said on
OL,12,FWednesday that a man who returned from
OL,13,FSouth America and traveled the cruise
OL,14,Fship tested positive for the virus and
OL,15,Fis receiving treatment.
OL,17,FThey could not specify when exactly
OL,18,Fthe patient was on board the MV
OL,19,FHondius.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
