OL,3,CThree people evacuated from hantavirus
OL,4,Cship amid Canary Islands row
OL,6,FHantavirus, is a rare disease
OL,7,Ftypically caused by contact with
OL,8,Finfected rodents' urine, faeces or
OL,9,Fsaliva, although earlier this week the
OL,10,FWHO suggested that rarer human-to-
OL,11,Fhuman transmission had taken place.
OL,13,FThe MV Hondius' set off from Ushuaia,
OL,14,FArgentina, on April 1, for a planned
OL,15,Fcruise of Antarctica and the South
OL,16,FAtlantic.
OL,18,FA passenger died on board on April 11,
OL,19,Foperator Oceanwide Expeditions said,
OL,20,Fadding that the cause of death could
OL,21,Fnot be determined on board.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778105470
OL,3,CThree people evacuated from hantavirus
OL,4,Cship amid Canary Islands row
OL,6,FThe Dutchman's body was taken off the
OL,7,Fvessel nearly two weeks later on the
OL,8,FBritish territory of St. Helena.
OL,10,FHis wife traveled by plane from St.
OL,11,FHelena to South Africa; collapsed at a
OL,12,FJohannesburg airport and died at a
OL,13,Fhospital on April 26, according to WHO
OL,14,Fand the South African Department of
OL,15,FHealth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778105470
OL,3,CThree people evacuated from hantavirus
OL,4,Cship amid Canary Islands row
OL,6,FThe ship sailed on to Ascension
OL,7,FIsland, an isolated Atlantic outpost
OL,8,Fabout 800 miles (1,300 kilometers) to
OL,9,Fthe north, where a sick British man
OL,10,Fwas taken off the ship and evacuated
OL,11,Ffirst to Ascension Island and then to
OL,12,FSouth Africa by plane.
OL,14,FHe is in intensive care in a South
OL,15,FAfrican hospital, according to WHO. A
OL,16,FGerman woman died on board the vessel
OL,17,Fon Saturday. At least four other
OL,18,Fpeople on board, including a British
OL,19,Fcrew member, have fallen sick.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778105470
OL,3,CThree people evacuated from hantavirus
OL,4,Cship amid Canary Islands row
OL,6,FFollowing the evacuations of suspected
OL,7,Fpatients, the current plan is for the
OL,8,Fship to sail to the Canary Islands,
OL,9,Fwhich will take three days of sailing,
OL,10,Faccording to the tour operator.
OL,12,FSpanish authorities will then conduct
OL,13,Fa full epidemiological investigation
OL,14,Fand full disinfection, said Dr Maria
OL,15,FVan Kerkhove, director for epidemic
OL,16,Fand pandemic preparedness and
OL,17,Fprevention for WHO.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778105470
OL,3,CThree people evacuated from hantavirus
OL,4,Cship amid Canary Islands row
OL,6,FThe Spanish health ministry said a
OL,7,Fdoctor from the MV Hondius who is "in
OL,8,Fserious condition" would be evacuated
OL,9,Fto the Canary Islands on Tuesday.
OL,11,FStrict health and safety procedures
OL,12,Fare currently in place on the ship,
OL,13,Fincluding isolation measures, hygiene
OL,14,Fprotocols and medical monitoring,
OL,15,FOceanwide Expeditions said.
OL,17,FIt added that the atmosphere on board
OL,18,Fthe ship "remains calm" and that
OL,19,Fpassengers were "generally composed".
OL,26,@oD@cOUpD@RO]zD@JOUzD@WO]{D@QOU{D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
