OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778105470
OL,3,CThree people evacuated from hantavirus
OL,4,Cship amid Canary Islands row
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FOne passenger, travel vlogger Jake
OL,12,FRosmarin, spoke of the fear and
OL,13,Funcertainty percolating through the
OL,14,Fship on Monday.
OL,16,F"What's happening right now is very
OL,17,Freal for all of us here. We're not
OL,18,Fjust a story. We're not just
OL,19,Fheadlines," he said in a video posted
OL,20,Fon Instagram, his voice cracking with
OL,21,Femotion.
OL,26,@xD@AOU{D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778105470
OL,3,CThree people evacuated from hantavirus
OL,4,Cship amid Canary Islands row
OL,6,FSocial distancing is being followed
OL,7,Fand passengers have the option for
OL,8,Fmeals to be delivered directly to
OL,9,Ftheir cabin, Rosmarin said in a
OL,10,Fstatement to ITV News' partner CNN on
OL,11,FTuesday.
OL,13,FAccess to the outer decks is permitted
OL,14,Ffor fresh air, but gathering in indoor
OL,15,Fareas such as the lounge is not
OL,16,Fallowed, he added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
