FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778105470
OL,3,CThree people evacuated from hantavirus
OL,4,Cship amid Canary Islands row
OL,6,F"Oceanwide Expeditions and the crew
OL,7,Fhave been doing everything within
OL,8,Ftheir ability to keep passengers safe,
OL,9,Finformed, and as comfortable as
OL,10,Fpossible during this time," he said.
OL,12,FBeyond the ship itself, authorities
OL,13,Fhave initiated contact tracing for
OL,14,Fthose on the flight to Johannesburg
OL,15,Fwith the Dutchwoman who later died.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@[O]
